cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI. 

This paper focuses on the coordination and control of drone swarms using visual inputs and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics), which deals with the design, construction, operation, and use of robots. The paper also heavily relies on computer vision techniques, such as convolutional neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with the coordination and control of multiple agents, which could also place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control).
